ion over it.";i:60;s:39:"If you build it they will come - Movie.";i:61;s:13:"Add the Base.";i:62;s:115:"Now that we have the cheat enabled build the walls of your garage and attach it all the way to the foundation wall.";i:63;s:92:"Please remember that the garage door is 4 squares long so make sure you have enough squares.";i:64;s:19:"I prefer 6 squares.";i:65;s:97:"Once you have placed your walls you will notice that the roof and walls look weird and funny see.";i:66;s:23:"Setting the Front Door.";i:67;s:98:"When I first built my house the door I wanted everyone to enter through was set at the Front Door.";i:68;s:75:"Now for some reason I cant even unset it I only get the options to lock it.";i:69;s:70:"I have 4 different entrances from the outside to get inside the house.";i:70;s:73:"The main entrance door and the back door only have the option to lock it.";}}